---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Software Development Case Studies | Real Results" 
  description="Real results from custom software development projects. See how we've helped businesses automate processes, build internal tools, and integrate systems. Actual time savings and ROI."
>
  <!-- Hero Section with Organic Blobs -->
  <section class="relative pt-20 md:pt-32 pb-32 md:pb-48 overflow-hidden">
    <!-- Organic Background Blobs -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-indigo/20 rounded-full blur-[80px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl relative z-10">
      <h1 class="font-display font-black text-6xl md:text-8xl tracking-tight leading-[0.95] text-ink dark:text-ink-dark mb-8 drop-shadow-sm">
        Case<br />
        <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Studies</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 max-w-2xl leading-relaxed font-medium">
        Real results from real businesses. See how we've helped teams automate repetitive work, build custom tools, and save time. <a href="/services" class="text-coral-vibrant hover:underline">Learn about our services</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Case Studies -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-24">
      
      <!-- Case Study 1: Gracelyn Group -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full text-coral-vibrant font-semibold text-sm">
            Professional Services
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
            Gracelyn Group:<br />
            <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Streamlined Reporting</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Gracelyn Group's incident reporting process was slow and manual. Staff needed a faster system that didn't require learning new procedures or disrupting their established workflow.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-coral rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Automated data capture and processing</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-coral rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Maintained familiar workflow patterns</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-coral rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Integrated with existing systems without disrupting workflows</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coral-vibrant">80%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Faster processing</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo">Zero</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Training required</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coral-vibrant">100%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">User adoption</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:order-last relative">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-12 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl shadow-coral/5 border border-coral/10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                Process Automation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
                Automated reporting workflow that removed manual steps while keeping the interface familiar to users.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Case Study 2: CareRev -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="lg:order-1 relative">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-12 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl shadow-indigo/5 border border-indigo/10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-indigo/20 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                Investigation Intelligence
              </h3>
              <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
                Improved auditor workflows that prioritize real threats and filter out false alarms automatically.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:order-2 space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-indigo/20 rounded-full text-indigo font-semibold text-sm">
            Healthcare Technology
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
            CareRev:<br />
            <span class="text-indigo italic">Smart Detection</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            CareRev's fraud team spent too much time reviewing false alerts and manually tracking suspicious patterns. They needed smarter tools to focus on real threats and investigate cases faster.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Pattern recognition system that identifies suspicious activity</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Faster investigation tools for auditors</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-indigo rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Removed hours of manual review work</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo">20hrs</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Saved weekly</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coral-vibrant">50%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">More efficient</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo">80%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Fewer false positives</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Case Study 3: Bug Reporting Integration -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full text-coral-vibrant font-semibold text-sm">
            Software Development
          </div>
          <h2 class="font-display font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
            Cross-Team<br />
            <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Communication</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
            Customer support and development teams were losing critical bug information in handoffs. Issues took too long to resolve because important details got lost between systems and teams.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-coral rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Connected previously disconnected internal systems</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-coral rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Preserved existing team workflows</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-coral rounded-full mt-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>
              <span class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 font-medium">Real-time information sharing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6 pt-6">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coral-vibrant">1 Day</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Faster resolution</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-indigo">20%</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Efficiency gain</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-coral-vibrant">75+</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-ink/60 dark:text-ink-dark/60">Team members</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:order-last relative">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-white/5 p-12 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl shadow-indigo/5 border border-indigo/10 relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-indigo/20 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
                Team Integration
              </h3>
              <p class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
                Connected systems so teams can collaborate without information getting stuck in silos.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Results Overview -->
  <section class="py-24 relative">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-indigo/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="text-center space-y-6 mb-20">
        <h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
          Results<br />
          <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">That Matter</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Real metrics from real businesses. These are actual results from companies that worked with us to automate their processes and build custom tools.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div class="text-center space-y-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-indigo/10 shadow-xl shadow-indigo/5">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-indigo">150+ Hours</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Weekly Time Savings</div>
          <div class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70">Consistent productivity gains</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center space-y-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-coral/10 shadow-xl shadow-coral/5">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-coral-vibrant">100%</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Client Satisfaction</div>
          <div class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70">Clients achieved their goals completely</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center space-y-4 p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white dark:bg-white/5 border border-indigo/10 shadow-xl shadow-indigo/5">
          <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-indigo">$400K</div>
          <div class="text-lg font-medium text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">Cost Savings</div>
          <div class="text-ink/70 dark:text-ink-dark/70">Delivered to our clients</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full overflow-hidden -z-10 pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-[10%] left-[-10%] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-coral-light/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[10%] right-[-5%] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-indigo/20 rounded-full blur-[100px] animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-10 relative z-10">
      <h2 class="font-display font-black text-5xl md:text-7xl tracking-tight text-ink dark:text-ink-dark">
        Ready to Join<br />
        <span class="text-coral-vibrant italic">Our Success Stories?</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-ink/80 dark:text-ink-dark/80 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Let's talk about how we can help your team automate repetitive work and get similar results. <a href="/services" class="text-coral-vibrant hover:underline">See our services</a> or <a href="/contact" class="text-coral-vibrant hover:underline">get in touch</a>.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-coral-vibrant text-white px-12 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg hover:bg-coral hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 shadow-xl shadow-coral/20">
        Start Your Success Story
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout> 